description:
Hello, I'm Agatha! 😊

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching :)

I'm excited to share this makeup tutorial with you because I'm also going to share my thoughts about the newest products from vice cosmetics which are the supemegaultra curl mascara and the kavogue full face palette. Let me know if you want to see more makeup tutorials like this 🥰

If you have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise)

KAVOGUE FULL FACE PALETTE - 395 but on sale for 345
